1.1.1. Integrate FCM Push1.1.2. Configure FCM information to the Tuya Iot platform1.1.3. The registered token is registered to Tuya Cloud.1.1.4. Receive and process messages1.2. User unbind1.2.1. Send Push1.2.2. Precautions1.1.1. Integrate FCM Push
Foreign users need to integrate Google’s FCM push service. According to official document,  Firebase is added to your Android project, then the client is configured by reference with  Android Client Configuration Firebase
